org.eclipse.graphiti.mm.algorithms.styles
Interface TextStyle

All Known Implementing Classes:
TextStyleImpl
public interface TextStyle

A representation of the model object 'Text Style'.

Since:
0.10

The following features are supported:

  • Underline
  • Underline Style
  • Strikeout
  • Font
  • Foreground
  • Background
  • Underline Color
  • Strikeout Color

See Also:
StylesPackage.getTextStyle()
